  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT6-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">varaiviṭai vaittup pirintavaḻi āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷ tōḻiyai neruṅkic colliyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken directed to the confidante by HER, who didn't have the strength [any more] when [he] had separated after the time for marriage had been fixed.</p>
          </div>

        <div xml:id="KT6">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>                naḷḷeṉ ṟaṉṟē yāmañ collavin</l>
<l>                tiṉitaṭaṅ kiṉarē mākkaṇ muṉiviṉṟu</l>
<l>                naṉantalai yulakamun tuñcu</l>
<l>                mōryāṉ maṉṟa tuñcā tēṉē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Deepest midnight. Wordless</l>
<l>sweetly still were the people. Sorrowless</l>
<l>the whole wide world is sleeping.</l>
<l>Only I, indeed, do not sleep.</l>
             </lg>
        </div>
